	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/054001a12609.jpg" width="600" height="437" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	扑克牌椅子 by Kevin Hviid&nbsp;
</h3>
<p>
	丹麦的设计师 Kevin Hviid 将他的四把椅子按扑克牌命名为：国王（K）、王后（Q）、侍从（J）和大师（A）。它们都是由轻质钢架做的，与对应字母有一个类似的外形或感觉。蓝色的椅子代表国王，超大的泡沫靠背象征国王的权利与自信。王后椅的座位用了舒适的皮革面料，正面看是宽阔的椅子，而从侧面看却只有一张纸的厚度，显示出椅子的轻盈和优雅。侍从椅和大师椅都更规整，接近日常的椅子了。<a href="http://www.kevinhviid.com/#/a-collection-of-chairs/" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/cf8a48ff7116.jpg" width="818" height="818" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/9d1e7e56f96a.jpg" width="818" height="818" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/bd52dc6f7a7d.jpg" width="818" height="818" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/d88867335351.jpg" width="818" height="818" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	猫咪幸运饼干 by Felissimo
</h3>
<p>
	招财猫常常代表着幸运，这家日本的原创设计网站 Felissimo 推出了猫版幸运饼干。三角形的饼干里包裹着手工木制的猫咪公仔，两两一组，只有指头大小。或者双掌合十或者像招财猫一样招手，或者眯着眼睛做不理人的呆萌状，爱猫的人一定不会错过。一套售价 2200 日元，<a href="http://www.felissimo.co.jp/chouclub_c/gcd425359/?bid=12262&xid=p_cri_fc_CHOE_lowa%26low%3Da" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/f463db83899c.jpg" width="580" height="277" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/b5ac49480f65.jpg" width="580" height="477" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/a07a7785dc47.jpg" width="500" height="423" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/1b918cfb7faf.jpg" width="500" height="341" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/9a7fd5b56282.jpg" width="500" height="318" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/b51d3ee94118.jpg" width="500" height="341" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	&nbsp;“XYZ 粘钩” by 250 设计
</h3>
<p>
	挂钩不仅仅是挂衣服或者袋子，也可以固定小物品。这些来自韩国 250 设计工作室的粘钩，就将普通的挂钩改成了“叉”型，且横竖皆可。因为硅胶材料拥有弹性，可以将小物件卡在中间，相当于一个放置小物品的地方。粘合胶垫经过水冲洗后可以重复使用，耐磨防水，适合厨房和浴室。这款挂钩有 5 种颜色，<a href="http://storefarm.naver.com/250/products/295444778" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/82a1a8ed62f6.jpg" width="818" height="577" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/7959a7e96722.jpg" width="818" height="577" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/0c65382777c2.jpg" width="818" height="577" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/ed80661c6d67.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/e8a1d920abdd.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Kevin Hviidcatch 蜂蜜包 by 蔡承融&amp;曾翊婷
</h3>
<p>
	这款印上了黄黑相间的条纹的户外包名叫蜂蜜包，它可以沿着拉链拆成一条 5 米长的拉链绳，在急救时派上用场。蜂蜜包里面内置泡棉，可以直接抱着包在水里漂浮，里面套上了一个内袋，能够在拉开拉链时不让东西散落，也可以真正做到防水。这款用高拉力做的尼龙布料的包只有 700 克，却能承担 15 公斤的重量，另有一款橙色，<a href="http://www.zeczec.com/projects/catch" target="_blank">目前正在众筹。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/1c5ecf199b10.jpg" width="800" height="433" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/934d66dd7dee.jpg" width="800" height="426" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/5d3d6297c430.jpg" width="800" height="436" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/91f29803df7e.jpg" width="559" height="672" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/b1d3218a32dd.jpg" width="625" height="684" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Wooly Mammoth by New Balance&nbsp;
</h3>
<p>
	这是 New Balance 为 ML999 款鞋型带来的新系列“Wooly Mammoth”，源于一种远古动物猛玛象，分别用了黑色、蓝色与灰蓝色的麂皮做鞋身，令人联想到猛犸象的肤色和其生活的北极，鞋底采用了 ABZORB 缓震材料，同时也有保暖御寒的功能。售价 130 美元。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/3a92cba64c47.jpg" width="1024" height="683" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/5279772a5d22.jpg" width="826" height="549" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
